org.geppetto.model.variables

Interface Variable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISynchable, Node
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    VariableImpl

    public interface Variable
extends Node
    A representation of the model object 'Variable'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Anonymous Types
    • Types
    • Initial Values
    • Static
    • Position
    See Also:
    VariablesPackage.getVariable()
